Privacy Policy for 'Shortcuts for Transcribers'

Last Updated: 01.01.2024

Collection and Use of Information

Our extension does not collect or store any personal user data. We prioritize user privacy and strive to ensure a safe and convenient experience for our users.

Access to Data

The extension may request access to certain resources such as the active tab, local storage, or specific websites. This access is solely used to provide the functionality of the extension and is not shared with third parties.

Changes to the Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to make changes to our privacy policy. Any changes will be posted on this page.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions regarding our privacy policy, please contact us at working-kyljmeeski@gmail.com.
